sequenceDiagram
  participant Svc as Service
  participant OTEL as OTEL Collector
  participant Backend as Tracing Backend (Jaeger)
  participant Export as Exporter

  Svc->>OTEL: Create spans (incoming HTTP request)
  Svc->>Exporter: Export spans/metrics (OTLP)
  Export-->>OTEL: OTLP data
  OTEL->>Backend: Forward traces
  Backend-->>User: Visualize traces in UI

  Note over Svc,OTEL: Instrumentation SDK (automatic + manual) produces context
